{"tid":853994,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS 12上線2周近5成的iOS設備運行","createTime":"2018-10-09T04:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T23:29:49.000Z","uid":109383,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a70e15b0d28628c2a2025842cdcb73db1a374a8d","tid":853994,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:42:20.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司iPhone和iPad的最新作業系統iOS 12，國外分析網站指出，其普及速度較去年的iOS 11更快。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司iPhone和iPad的最新作業系統iOS 12，台灣於上月18日正式開放更新，現在據外國分析網站的統計，已經有大約47.6％的iOS設備是運行iOS 12。<br />\n據外媒《Tech Crunch》引述國外分析網站Mixpanel統計資料報導，目前已有約47.6％的iOS設備是運行iOS 12，約45.6％的iOS設備仍是運行iOS 11，而約6.9％的iOS設備則是運行更舊的版本。<br />\n據了解，上一代作業系統iOS 11要達到這樣的水準花了更多時間，去年蘋果在11月6日宣布，iOS 11比iOS 10來的更受歡迎。今年可以看出變化，過去用戶經常覺得舊的設備更新到新的iOS作業系統，會使設備變得較慢，但這次iOS 12聲稱專注在性能上，蘋果公司針對舊設備的更新進行優化。報導更是直接指出，若你是使用舊的iOS設備，若想獲得更快的使用體驗，建議升級iOS 12。"},{"pid":"7ab5e12bd0356154e66a3b43e9ea6ef3d9f43f88","tid":853994,"uid":12628,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"11嘅民怨大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw, 12嘅耗電問題幾時改善，屌下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341aa8e5dfa8530bc9d1e1c252476f253383858a","tid":853994,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:58:16.000Z","msg":"快唔快得過高階電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424da78a139131a88042c4efb2af88995579568c","tid":853994,"uid":109383,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"341aa8e5dfa8530bc9d1e1c252476f253383858a","tid":853994,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:58:16.000Z","msg":"快唔快得過高階電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"快過android機已足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/no